Ensures valid, complete, rule-consistent reasoning.

Conceptual Integrity

Stability Floor (∆H) + integrity monitors

Prevents representational fragmentation.

Consistency

Zero-Variance Output

Same input → same output. Guaranteed.

These invariants are enforced before DI² is even allowed to generate.

